msgstr "微内核的安全性，宏内核的速度。"

#: src/kernel/the-framekernel-architecture.md:7
msgid ""
"Asterinas introduces a novel OS architecture called _framekernel_, which "
"unleashes the full power of Rust to bring the best of both monolithic "
"kernels and microkernels."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas推出了一种名为\n"
"*framekernel*的新型操作系统架构，该架构充分发挥Rust的强大能力，融合了宏内核和"
"微内核的优势。"

#: src/kernel/the-framekernel-architecture.md:11
msgid ""
"Within the framekernel architecture, the entire OS resides in the same "
"address space (like a monolithic kernel) and is required to be written in "
"Rust. However, there's a twist---the kernel is partitioned in two halves: "
"the OS Framework (akin to a microkernel) and the OS Services. Only the OS "
"Framework is allowed to use _unsafe Rust_, while the OS Services must be "
"written exclusively in _safe Rust_."
msgstr ""
"在framekernel架构中，整个操作系统驻留在同一地址空间中（类似于宏内核），并且必"
"须使用Rust编写。不过，这里有一个特别之处——内核被分为两半：操作系统框架（类似"
"微内核）和操作系统服务。只有操作系统框架允许使用*不安全的Rust*，而操作系统服"
"务必须完全使用*安全的Rust*编写。"

